{"tid":206061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨陳家偉幫襯「斷正」","createTime":"2017-04-18T07:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T11:53:41.000Z","uid":50391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e766468849f74c3b69f4663239078a0fff9739","tid":206061,"uid":50391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香檳大廈以鳳樓聞名，亦有名人身陷鳳樓醜聞。二○一一年七月十二日，時任民主黨總幹事、前九龍城區議會副主席陳家偉，被發現進入香檳大廈一間鳳樓，他在鳳姐房間逗留四十分鐘後，離開時遭本報記者撞正，即時狼狽逃跑，最終「走唔甩」垂頭喪氣坐在街邊，被質問時支吾以對，一時稱背黨瞞妻光顧鳳樓，一時辯稱找鳳姐「訪談」，又承認鳳姐全身赤裸，在他要求下擺出各種性愛姿勢，他僅在旁提點何謂安全性行為，聲稱自己與鳳姐無身體接觸，不過其後有嫖客踢爆陳講大話。<br />\n<br />\n佢得罪左東方？<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170418/00176_010.html?pubdate=20170418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170418%2F00176_010.html%3Fpubdate%3D20170418&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a9208afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170418/00176_010.html?pubdate=20170418</a>"},{"pid":"670946a102d1ae56fcb3760c4af57d5403bcd2d9","tid":206061,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:55:05.000Z","msg":"叫雞又唔係犯法，有咩問題姐"},{"pid":"ccfd3a26962a3630dfb50af4e3e7316a42e07a89","tid":206061,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"廁紙包頭衝！"},{"pid":"ffd1c8ad59851b808e3ad86d0dfb6772bc019d9b","tid":206061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫雞又唔係犯法，有咩問題姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係, 學云伯直認叫雞咪得囉"},{"pid":"6878be2d364c13a2645c5a8b9c9577fc348c08b4","tid":206061,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7587213b19865f7479be51a97c0e8936025b8198","tid":206061,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"佢支持陀地 應記一功<br />\n果然係本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/n